description: Gets a list of Amazon S3 Storage Lens configurations. For more information about S3 Storage Lens, see Assessing your storage activity and usage with Amazon S3 Storage Lens in the Amazon S3 User Guide.

parameters.name: AccountId
parameters.description: The account ID of the requester.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the request produced more than the maximum number of S3 Storage Lens configuration results, you can pass this value into a subsequent request to retrieve the next page of results.

nested_items.name: StorageLensConfigurationList
nested_items.description: A list of S3 Storage Lens configurations.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: A container for the S3 Storage Lens configuration ID.

nested_items.name: StorageLensArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the S3 Storage Lens configuration. This property is read-only.

nested_items.name: HomeRegion
nested_items.description: A container for the S3 Storage Lens home Region. Your metrics data is stored and retained in your designated S3 Storage Lens home Region.

nested_items.name: IsEnabled
nested_items.description: A container for whether the S3 Storage Lens configuration is enabled. This property is required.
